episodes.title: I accidentally joined a cult
episodes.description:
Let’s talk about the Boston Church of Christ and how it’s actually a cult. It took me a while to realize it but once I actually sat down and processed what life was like and how limited I was, I realized what was going on. I started deep diving and realized I wasn’t the only person to experience this.
